akka.typed.testkit

Class Inbox<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.typed.testkit.Inbox<T>

  • public class Inbox<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility for receiving messages outside of an actor. No methods are provided for synchronously awaiting a message, this is primarily useful for synchronous tests of behaviors that send messages to other actors, where an Inbox&rsquo;s ActorRef can conveniently be used as a stub.
